dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Includes distance table and 2 inset maps (Continuation of Aleutian Islands -- From Juneau to Forty Mile Creek). From: Report of the governor of the district of Alaska to the Secretary of the Interior. 1903.
